layout: Layout
title: "Services | Handyman Cruz"
description: "Explore the wide range of reliable, local handyman services I offer."
---

<section class="relative h-[70vh] bg-fixed bg-center bg-cover" style="background-image: url('/assets/services-hero.jpg');">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60"></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center text-white h-full px-4">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight drop-shadow-lg">My Services</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-xl drop-shadow">Craftsmanship that lasts. Local service you can trust.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 space-y-16">

  <section class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <a href="/services/general-repairs" class="group bg-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-6 shadow hover:shadow-xl transition">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-yellow-300 mb-2">General Repairs</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300">Fixing doors, taps, walls — you name it. Quick and clean.</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/services/tiling-grouting" class="group bg-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-6 shadow hover:shadow-xl transition">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-yellow-300 mb-2">Tiling & Grouting</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300">Cracks? Gaps? Re-grouting that stays sealed and clean.</p>
    </a>

    <a href="/services/concreting-paving" class="group bg-neutral-800 rounded-lg p-6 shadow hover:shadow-xl transition">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-yellow-300 mb-2">Concreting & Paving</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-300">Solid slabs, clean paths, or paved patios — built to last.</p>
    </a>
  </section>

  <div class="text-center">
    <a href="/#quote" class="inline-block bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded shadow transition">
      Request a Free Quote
    </a>
  </div>
</main>
